e opening by selecting the[Start]button -> [Battle]button)\n2.GamePlay\nOnce started, the move is automatic.\nWe will command the two Shikigami.\n3.GameOver\nIf both Shikigami are defeated, the game is over.\n4.GameClear\nThe game is cleared when the boss is defeated.", "short_description": "Japanese-style command-type action game.\nYou will command the two Shikigami.\nThe coalescing attack is exhilarating.\nPlease experience the Youkai tale!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.atsiaito.com/privacypolicy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "atsi_aito", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.atsiaito.com/product/houteishikix", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ADVENTURE", "NARRATIVE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "480945406758278"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "355959179665523"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "355959179665523"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1637190360, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "355959179665523"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "4398519016924010", "version": "1.5"}, "id": "624273618553396", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "bi